name: TRIP REPORT | Yukon's Airline! Air North Boeing 737-500 Edmonton to Calgary
description:
Air North is a northern Canadian airline based in Whitehorse, Yukon, and operates a fleet of Boeing 737s, ATRs, and Hawker Siddeley HS 748s. Air North serves Alberta via a triangle routing, flying Whitehorse-Edmonton-Calgary-Whitehorse, and the Edmonton-Calgary segment is bookable. See what I thought of "Yukon's Airline" in this video on board their Boeing 737-500!

Thanks for watching!
